{
  "id": "adv_event_2204_01_01",
  "title": "一番好きな曲",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ！　麻奈様っ！　何度見ても素敵過ぎますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Mana-sama! You're always too wonderful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 7.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "やはり、麻奈様こそが、究極かつ至高のアイドル……！\n私が心奪われた、唯一無二のアイドルオブアイドルズ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Indeed‚ Mana-sama is the ultimate and supreme idol…!\nThe one and only idol of idols who captured my heart!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.4,
      "endTime": 19.2183785121,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12400
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12866.6666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 19.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃーん、おっはよー！\nって、今日も相変わらず麻奈ちゃんのライブ映像だねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan‚ good morning!\nOh‚ today's Mana-chan's live footage again‚ huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4,
      "endTime": 29.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 29.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "当然ですわ！　麻奈様のライブ観戦は\n私の日課なのですから！　きゃーっ！　麻奈様ーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course! Watching Mana-sama's live is\nmy daily routine! Kyaa! Mana-sama!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9,
      "endTime": 40.284240722599996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 36.3
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 40.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "今朝はLizNoirと合同でダンスレッスンだから\n早めに出るって言ったのに……まだ準備もしてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We have joint dance lessons with LizNoir this morning‚\nso I said we should leave early… but I'm not even ready yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5,
      "endTime": 49.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "遅刻したら、莉央さん達に悪いでしょ\n早く行こう。芽衣も手伝って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It would be bad to be late and inconvenience Rio-san and the others.\nLet's go quickly. Mei‚ help too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.4,
      "endTime": 55.666666666699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "了解だよー！\nほらほら、すずにゃんレッスン行くよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood!\nCome on‚ Suzu-nyan‚ let's go to the lesson~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.9666666667,
      "endTime": 60.9554875056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 57.5
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 61.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ああっ！　待って下さい！\n今朝はまだ三回しか観ていませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! Please wait!\nI've only watched it three times this morning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1666666667,
      "endTime": 66.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 66.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "三回観れば十分でしょ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Three times should be enough‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.5,
      "endTime": 69,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 69.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、すずにゃん、いい子だから聞き分けてね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay okay‚ Suzu-nyan‚ be a good girl and listen‚ okay~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2,
      "endTime": 73.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 74.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっ、今から、私の一番好きな曲が！\n『Precious』が！　せめてこの曲だけでも～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ my favorite song is playing now!\n\"Precious\"! At least let me listen to this song~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0666666667,
      "endTime": 82.1333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 82.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ダメよ、電車に乗り遅れちゃう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ we'll miss the train.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3,
      "endTime": 85.1923128128,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 85.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "帰ってからのお楽しみってことで～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's save it for when we get back home~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.4,
      "endTime": 88.1810431004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyosuzroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dormitory",
      "startTime": 88.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈様のご尊顔が遠のく～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-sama's precious face is getting farther away~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.3666666667,
      "endTime": 93.3333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-close-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4524.215698199995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "1、2！　1、2！\n指先まで意識して！　疲れを表情に出さない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "1‚ 2! 1‚ 2!\nBe conscious of your fingertips! Don't show your fatigue on your face!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.7666666667,
      "endTime": 102.0601587931,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "は、はい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-Yes!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.3333333333,
      "endTime": 103.9539455652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "うわ～っ、やっぱ、莉央さんカッコいい～！\n芽衣もっと近くで見たい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ Rio-san is so cool~!\nMei want to see up close too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9666666667,
      "endTime": 113.5666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと、近過ぎよ！　かえって見にくいでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ you're too close! It's actually harder to see!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.7,
      "endTime": 117.59340143200001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、指先は近くの方が分かりやすいです\nなるほど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's easier to see the fingertips up close.\nI see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.8,
      "endTime": 124.7068482399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃まで？　ああ、もうしょうがない子達ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even you‚ Kotono? Oh well‚ these kids…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.9,
      "endTime": 129.93333333340001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……やっぱりみんなレベルは相当上がっているな\nそうなると、何を基準にすべきか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Everyone's level has definitely risen.\nIn that case‚ what should be the standard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.0333333333,
      "endTime": 140.89999999990002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はい、十分休憩よ\n各自、水分を摂って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ enough of a break.\nEveryone‚ hydrate yourselves.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.6,
      "endTime": 148.929296875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、莉央さん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ Rio-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.3333333333,
      "endTime": 151.1307936986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2204_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "何？　すず、気になることでもあった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? Is there something bothering you‚ Suzu?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3333333333,
      "endTime": 154.2532879193,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
